            <title><![CDATA[Genesis RPG Traysia coming to PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, Switch, and PC on April 24]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/04/genesis-rpg-traysia-coming-to-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-xbox-one-switch-and-pc-on-april-24</link>
            <guid>1483117</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><a title="Companies > Ratalaika Games [40 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/ratalaika-games">Ratalaika Games</a> and <a title="Companies > Shinyuden [23 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/shinyuden">Shinyuden</a> will release Telenet Japan-developed, 1992-released Genesis RPG <em><a title="Games > Traysia" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/traysia">Traysia</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4365530/Traysia/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on April 24, the companies announced. <span id="more-1038491"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via Ratalaika Games and Shinyuden:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>Dreaming of becoming a world-traveling <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,912 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure</a>r, a young boy named Roy left his hometown. Having known neither travel nor battle, the boy’s adventure now begins.</p><p>After behind the hometown, he traveled through many mountains and forests. Roy finally arrived at a small county called Kingdom of Salon.</p><p>Traysia is a girl waiting for Roy to come back in their hometown, Johanna, a port town.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><em>Traysia</em> is a full-scale <a title="Genres > RPG [18,071 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg">role-playing game</a> made up of five scenarios, offering a definitive fantasy romance of love and adventure.</p><p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul><li>Rewind/Turbo function: repeat something until you achieve perfection, or speed things up.</li><li>Save state function: save wherever you want to in the game, and restart from that exact point.</li><li>Screen filters: select from several filters to modify how the game looks (retro-style monitor, black-and-white, etc.).</li><li>Gallery: view images from the original game’s manual and box design.</li><li>Cheats function: activate cheats that will make your mission a lot easier (infinite lives, invulnerability, etc.).</li><li>Jukebox: listen to the 21 music tracks included in the game whenever you want.</li></ul><p>This game is re-release of <em>Traysia</em>, which the first launched in 1992s for home consoles.</p></blockquote></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/04/genesis-rpg-traysia-coming-to-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-xbox-one-switch-and-pc-on-april-24]]></content:encoded>
