      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Starfield [17 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/starfield">Starfield</a></em>&nbsp;for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <em><a title="Games > Pokemon Champions [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pokemon-champions">Pokemon Champions</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>&nbsp;are the highlights of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-1038434"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are <em><a title="Games > Memories Off Sousou: Break out of my shell [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/memories-off-sousou-break-out-of-my-shell">Memories Off Sousou: Break out of my shell</a></em> for PlayStation 5, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, Switch, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, and <em><a title="Games > TAMASHIKA [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/tamashika">TAMASHIKA</a></em> for PlayStation 5, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, Switch, and PC.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through <a title="Companies > Playasia" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playasia">Play-Asia</a> links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU2025</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><em>Auerole: Wings of Hope</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/aureole-wings-of-hope-multi-language/13/70jcqp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>) – Already available digitally worldwide.<ul><li>Limited Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/aureole-wings-of-hope-limited-edition-multi-language/13/70jcqv?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>)</li></ul><!-- AD: content -->
